Opportunities

Multi-Unit Acquisition
Jack in the Box Inc. (JACK) is offering a unique opportunity to franchise with one of the most popular brands in the quick-serve restaurant (“QSR”) industry. The company’s emphasis on operational efficiency and franchisee-focused value innovation has led JACK to become one of the most respected and sought after brands in the industry. The company is looking to establish relationships with select multi-unit franchise operators of non-competitive brands to franchise our brand in emerging and core markets.

Available Markets



Not Released
Collecting interest opportunities applications
Available
Open franchising opportunities in the state
Not Seeking
Market sold or no opportunities available in the state






Minimum franchisee qualifications (per group):

Minimum of 5-years of multi-unit restaurant operating experience within the last 7 years
Minimum liquidity requirements for the Franchisee or its Owners (as a whole) are as follows:

$250,000 (1-2 units)
$500,000 (3 + units)
$750,000 (developers)

Minimum net worth of $1,500,000
Ability to develop at least 5 restaurants
Operator is an equity partner
Real estate development experience
Passion for the restaurant industry

Your use of this site constitutes your agreement to these terms and conditions. None of the communications made through this website should be construed as an offer to sell any franchise in, nor is any such communication directed to the residents of, any jurisdiction requiring registration of the franchise before it is offered or sold in the jurisdiction. No franchises will be sold to any resident of any such jurisdiction until the offer has been exempted from the requirements, or duly registered in such jurisdiction and the required Franchise Disclosure Document has been delivered to the prospective franchisee in compliance with applicable law.
